{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were fully aware of it, that there is no such thing that they are going to put you in a worse camp, or in a worse position.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they you didn't obey something, they shoot at you without any warning or without any questions, without any problem.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The shooting was every-day affair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every day you heard-- a the gun, the machine gun going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It-- it-- it wasn't news.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day when I-- when I-- when I come to that camp, maybe I should describe exactly what was the reason why I got-- go into the personal--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the twin camp, the [GERMAN] camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was that-- not-- not only what we see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What we saw, what what we heard it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the moaning and the groaning and the yelling and the screaming and the begging.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's-- it's-- it's little boys or little girls, or grown-up people, old people, regardless who-- who was basically there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And through-- they had-- they had barracks which had windows.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have any windows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had barracks with windows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and we thought from tearing at each other and yelling at each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we saw that-- we heard the tremendous-- I mean, the pain, what these people had to go through, that must have been beyond any human pain.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Beyond what-- what they-- And we have seen, sometimes, outside, people walking with-- naturally they didn't have any gauze or any-- or and sterile way of doing it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But people half naked, walking-- walking around with a rag or something, covering up their wound.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some of them collapsing, some of them, many of them, going against the wire.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
